{
  "stem": "26983.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Auschwitz-- Birkenau, because we're anyhow-- we had to die.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the Germans said, we don't care what you do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Do it in the best way which you and us should profit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we knew-- we knew we have in our Kartotek six months.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we knew later on, of course, when the whole transport went to gas.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we knew afterwards who, and what, and how it happens.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I want to tell you a little about this-- famous children camp, number 31.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We sang songs-- let's say one tune-- was the whole years I will-- and I tried to ask people who know music from varied camps.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because I was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'Dona Nobis Pacem'.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And only-- [LAUGHS] about a year ago, somebody who is a singer and knows very, very old German songs said, well, that's a old Lutheran--",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SINGING 'DONA NOBIS PACEM'] Dona, nobis, pacem.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Dona, nobis, pacem.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we-- were singing from the 9th Symphony, as I mentioned a previous time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We performed it for the Germans sometimes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if the German didn't like it-- especially our-- the head of our camp was a German Reich Deutsche with a green triangle-- Arno Bohm.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had number 8-- he was a kill-- a real-- criminal.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If he didn't like something, he took his whistle and-- [LAUGHS] stop.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Later on, Willy Brachmann, who was his kapo of the camp, took over.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the other kapo was Ada Fischer, who was the hangman from Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I told you about the hanging.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was a very strange man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He said, I will do it, because for me, it's easy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he liked the children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "To us--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was, I think, Czech-- Czech from Prague or somewhere.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in our camp, he became a kapo of the camp later.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
